      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks that's a good start. maybe we could make it a little less \"template-y\"? i want it to feel like it's coming from a human, not just a standard HR bot. can you add a sentence or two that acknowledges how much effort they put into the technical assessment specifically?",
      "source": "evaluator"
